<li id="cite_note-33"><b><a href="#cite_ref-33" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFDichter">Dichter, T.. <a href="http://www.legalcity.net/Index.cfm?fuseaction=MAGAZINE.article&amp;ArticleID=8803808" class="external text" title="http://www.legalcity.net/Index.cfm?fuseaction=MAGAZINE.article&amp;ArticleID=8803808" rel="nofollow">"Hype and Hope: The Worrisome State of the Microcredit Movement"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Consultative_Group_to_Assist_the_Poor_(CGAP)" title="Consultative Group to Assist the Poor (CGAP)">Consultative Group to Assist the Poor (CGAP)</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.legalcity.net/Index.cfm?fuseaction=MAGAZINE.article&amp;ArticleID=8803808" class="external free" title="http://www.legalcity.net/Index.cfm?fuseaction=MAGAZINE.article&amp;ArticleID=8803808" rel="nofollow">http://www.legalcity.net/Index.cfm?fuseaction=MAGAZINE.article&amp;ArticleID=8803808</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Hype+and+Hope%3A+The+Worrisome+State+of+the+Microcredit+Movement&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Dichter&amp;rft.aufirst=T.&amp;rft.au=Dichter%2C+T.&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BConsultative+Group+to+Assist+the+Poor+%28CGAP%29%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legalcity.net%2FIndex.cfm%3Ffuseaction%3DMAGAZINE.article%26ArticleID%3D8803808&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Microfinance"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-34"><b><a href="#cite_ref-34" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFLittlefieldMorduch.2C_Jonathan_and_Hashemi.2C_Syed">Littlefield, Elizabeth; Morduch, Jonathan and Hashemi, Syed (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2003-01-01"><a href="/wiki/2003" title="2003">2003</a>-<a href="/wiki/January_1" title="January 1">01-01</a></span>). "<a href="http://www.cgap.org/docs/FocusNote_24.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.cgap.org/docs/FocusNote_24.pdf" rel="nofollow">Is Microfinance an Effective Strategy to Reach the Millennium Development Goals?</a>" (pdf). <i>FocusNote</i> (Consultative Group to Assist the Poor) (24)<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.cgap.org/docs/FocusNote_24.pdf" class="external free" title="http://www.cgap.org/docs/FocusNote_24.pdf" rel="nofollow">http://www.cgap.org/docs/FocusNote_24.pdf</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-03-27</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Is+Microfinance+an+Effective+Strategy+to+Reach+the+Millennium+Development+Goals%3F&amp;rft.jtitle=FocusNote&amp;rft.aulast=Littlefield&amp;rft.aufirst=Elizabeth&amp;rft.au=Littlefield%2C+Elizabeth&amp;rft.au=Morduch%2C+Jonathan+and+Hashemi%2C+Syed&amp;rft.date=%5B%5B2003-01-01%5D%5D&amp;rft.issue=24&amp;rft.pub=Consultative+Group+to+Assist+the+Poor&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cgap.org%2Fdocs%2FFocusNote_24.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Microfinance"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-35"><b><a href="#cite_ref-35" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFMorduch">Morduch, Jonathan (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2008-10-17"><a href="/wiki/2008" title="2008">2008</a>-<a href="/wiki/October_17" title="October 17">10-17</a></span>). <a href="http://www.philanthropyaction.com/nc/cutting_edge_research_on_microfinance/" class="external text" title="http://www.philanthropyaction.com/nc/cutting_edge_research_on_microfinance/" rel="nofollow">"Comments Made at IPA/FAI Microfinance Conference Oct. 17 2008"</a>. Philanthropy Action<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.philanthropyaction.com/nc/cutting_edge_research_on_microfinance/" class="external free" title="http://www.philanthropyaction.com/nc/cutting_edge_research_on_microfinance/" rel="nofollow">http://www.philanthropyaction.com/nc/cutting_edge_research_on_microfinance/</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-10-17</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Comments+Made+at+IPA%2FFAI+Microfinance+Conference+Oct.+17+2008&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Morduch&amp;rft.aufirst=Jonathan&amp;rft.au=Morduch%2C+Jonathan&amp;rft.date=%5B%5B2008-10-17%5D%5D&amp;rft.pub=Philanthropy+Action&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.philanthropyaction.com%2Fnc%2Fcutting_edge_research_on_microfinance%2F&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Microfinance"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-36"><b><a href="#cite_ref-36" title="">^</a></b> Westover J. (2008). <a href="http://www.sociology.org/content/2008/_westover_finance.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.sociology.org/content/2008/_westover_finance.pdf" rel="nofollow">The Record of Microfinance: The Effectiveness/Ineffectiveness of Microfinance Programs as a Means of Alleviating Poverty</a>. <i>Electronic Journal of Sociology]]</i>.</li>
<li id="cite_note-37"><b><a href="#cite_ref-37" title="">^</a></b> Kim, J.C., Watts, C. H., Hargreaves, J. R., Ndhlovu, L. X., Phetla, G., Morison, L. A., et al. (2007). Understanding the impact of a microfinance-based intervention of women’s empowerment and the reduction of intimate partner violence in South Africa. American Journal of Public Health.</li>
