<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Microfinance&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.microlinks.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.microlinks.org/" rel="nofollow">microLINKS</a>, - a knowledge-sharing family of applications and tools designed to improve the impact of USAID microenterprise programs and activities.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.cgap.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.cgap.org/" rel="nofollow">CGAP</a>, Consultative Group to Assist the Poor</li>
<li><a href="http://www.fdc.org.au" class="external text" title="http://www.fdc.org.au" rel="nofollow">The Foundation for Development Cooperation</a> - Asia-Pacific Microfinance Specialist NGO</li>
<li><a href="http://www.mra.gov.bd/" class="external text" title="http://www.mra.gov.bd/" rel="nofollow">MRA</a>, The central body to monitor and supervise microfinance operation of Non-government organizations of Bangladesh</li>
<li><a href="http://www.financialaccess.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.financialaccess.org/" rel="nofollow">Financial Access Initiative</a>, a joint program of Harvard, Yale, New York University and Innovations for Poverty Action</li>
<li><a href="http://aede.osu.edu/programs/RuralFinance/" class="external text" title="http://aede.osu.edu/programs/RuralFinance/" rel="nofollow">Rural Finance Program</a> at <a href="/wiki/The_Ohio_State_University" title="The Ohio State University" class="mw-redirect">The Ohio State University</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.uncdf.org/mfdl/index.php?_mode=students.home" class="external text" title="http://www.uncdf.org/mfdl/index.php?_mode=students.home" rel="nofollow">UNCDF Microfinance Distance Learning Program</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.onehen.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.onehen.org/" rel="nofollow">Teaching microfinance to kids - OneHen.org</a></li>
<li><a href="http://blackandwhiteprogram.com/report/what-microfinance-means-for-china%e2%80%99s-growth" class="external text" title="http://blackandwhiteprogram.com/report/what-microfinance-means-for-china%e2%80%99s-growth" rel="nofollow">Microfinance in China</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.indiamicrofinance.com/2008/12/microfinance-india-state-of-sector_12.html" class="external text" title="http://www.indiamicrofinance.com/2008/12/microfinance-india-state-of-sector_12.html" rel="nofollow">Microfinance India - State of the sector report 2006, 2007, 2008</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.luxflag.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.luxflag.org/" rel="nofollow">Luxembourg Fund Labelling Agency for Microfinance Investment Vehicles</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.mykro.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.mykro.org/" rel="nofollow">myKRO.org - Exploring the World of Microfinance</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.bwtp.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.bwtp.org/" rel="nofollow">The Banking with the Poor Network</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.microcapital.org/" class="external text" title="http://www.microcapital.org/" rel="nofollow">MicroCapital - The only source for daily, original, and substantiated microfinance news since 2005</a></li>
</ul>


